1
00:00:42,679 --> 00:00:43,759
We're closed for today.

2
00:00:46,039 --> 00:00:48,600
Have you seen this before?

3
00:00:50,200 --> 00:00:51,240
For items without an appointment,

4
00:00:51,840 --> 00:00:52,320
I won't look at them.

5
00:00:52,759 --> 00:00:54,799
You've appraised so many antiques,

6
00:00:54,960 --> 00:00:57,159
The Key of Fate that can swap destinies,

7
00:00:57,159 --> 00:00:58,159
have you seen it?

8
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:01,320
We only verify authenticity here.

9
00:01:02,280 --> 00:01:03,479
As for what you're describing,

10
00:01:03,799 --> 00:01:05,159
I suggest you try somewhere else.

11
00:01:06,959 --> 00:01:08,079
This is the thing

12
00:01:08,560 --> 00:01:10,439
that let Zhang Xiaobei steal your woman,

13
00:01:10,640 --> 00:01:11,480
your status,

14
00:01:11,799 --> 00:01:12,799
and your money.

15
00:01:14,439 --> 00:01:15,239
What are you talking about?

16
00:01:15,359 --> 00:01:16,120
I'm saying

17
00:01:16,439 --> 00:01:18,079
you're the real Sheng Yuanzhou.

18
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:21,519
Please leave.

19
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:22,920
We're about to close.

20
00:01:25,680 --> 00:01:27,799
Just take one bite with this spoon,

21
00:01:28,280 --> 00:01:29,400
and you'll understand everything.

22
00:01:29,719 --> 00:01:30,879
What kind of joke is this?

23
00:01:35,040 --> 00:01:36,159
Why don't you try it?

24
00:01:36,799 --> 00:01:38,640
It's just a bite of food.

25
00:01:53,799 --> 00:01:55,359
You stole my identity.

26
00:01:55,560 --> 00:01:56,640
You stole my money.

27
00:01:56,640 --> 00:01:58,000
You even stole Lin Siqi.

28
00:01:58,239 --> 00:01:59,719
How do you know all that?

29
00:02:01,480 --> 00:02:02,760
My Father has already given

30
00:02:02,760 --> 00:02:03,879
the Key of Fate to me.

31
00:02:06,400 --> 00:02:07,159
I'm telling you,

32
00:02:08,120 --> 00:02:09,680
Sheng Shizhong isn't a good person.

33
00:02:10,439 --> 00:02:11,639
He's not even your real family.

34
00:02:14,240 --> 00:02:16,080
A life of hardship tortured me.

35
00:02:16,479 --> 00:02:19,080
My girlfriend left me because I was poor.

36
00:02:19,439 --> 00:02:20,919
I don't want to live like this anymore.

37
00:02:21,319 --> 00:02:22,080
Even though

38
00:02:22,840 --> 00:02:24,240
I've let my parents down,

39
00:02:25,319 --> 00:02:26,960
I don't have the courage to go on living.

40
00:02:28,639 --> 00:02:30,719
I'm taking some people to hell with me.

41
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:37,439
Yuanzhou,

42
00:02:37,879 --> 00:02:38,479
you go out first.

43
00:02:39,199 --> 00:02:40,400
Yes, Father.

44
00:02:47,759 --> 00:02:49,319
Stop wasting your effort.

45
00:02:50,199 --> 00:02:50,960
This place

46
00:02:51,599 --> 00:02:53,199
is where you'll die.

47
00:02:58,520 --> 00:03:00,319
You ungrateful traitor.

48
00:03:00,560 --> 00:03:01,680
I treated you like my son,

49
00:03:01,680 --> 00:03:02,960
and you want to hurt me?

50
00:03:07,080 --> 00:03:07,680
Ridiculous.

51
00:03:08,639 --> 00:03:10,240
You're obviously just like me,

52
00:03:10,240 --> 00:03:11,599
coveting someone else's life,

53
00:03:11,919 --> 00:03:13,840
yet you insist on disguising yourself

54
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:15,719
as so noble.

55
00:03:19,280 --> 00:03:20,759
Have you always thought

56
00:03:22,120 --> 00:03:23,360
the life I stole

57
00:03:23,360 --> 00:03:25,080
was never meant to be mine?

58
00:03:26,120 --> 00:03:28,560
Then is Sheng Yuanzhou's life yours?

59
00:03:29,280 --> 00:03:31,400
I'll make you give everything

60
00:03:31,400 --> 00:03:32,000
back to him right now.

61
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:38,159
This is a new toxin I bought overseas.

62
00:03:38,599 --> 00:03:39,319
It acts fast,

63
00:03:39,680 --> 00:03:40,599
and it won't be too painful.

64
00:03:41,120 --> 00:03:42,159
Once you're dead,

65
00:03:42,680 --> 00:03:44,919
I'll be Sheng Shizhong forever.

66
00:03:45,879 --> 00:03:46,800
After midnight,

67
00:03:46,800 --> 00:03:48,280
it's your Auto-Reset Day.

68
00:03:48,639 --> 00:03:51,120
You and Sheng Yuanzhou will switch back.

69
00:03:51,360 --> 00:03:53,039
Just now I already had Sheng Yuanzhou

70
00:03:53,039 --> 00:03:54,360
put on your clothes

71
00:03:54,599 --> 00:03:55,879
and record a video will.

72
00:03:58,919 --> 00:03:59,800
Stop struggling.

73
00:04:00,039 --> 00:04:02,120
After everyone sees that video,

74
00:04:02,120 --> 00:04:03,759
they'll think you, Zhang Xiaobei,

75
00:04:03,759 --> 00:04:06,280
killed yourself over heartbreak.

76
00:04:09,280 --> 00:04:11,599
The glorious moment is almost here.

77
00:04:23,399 --> 00:04:23,839
Father,

78
00:04:24,480 --> 00:04:25,439
some security guards are at the door.

79
00:04:28,519 --> 00:04:30,480
Have they found out?

80
00:04:33,959 --> 00:04:34,600
Keep an eye on him.

81
00:04:41,839 --> 00:04:42,240
What's wrong?

82
00:04:42,920 --> 00:04:43,279
Sir.

83
00:04:43,720 --> 00:04:45,399
Your car's taking the spot next door.

84
00:04:45,639 --> 00:04:46,879
We've gotten several complaints already.

85
00:04:47,279 --> 00:04:48,399
Please go move it right away.

86
00:04:49,759 --> 00:04:50,560
Sheng Yuanzhou.

87
00:04:51,720 --> 00:04:52,680
Sheng Yuanzhou.

88
00:04:53,399 --> 00:04:54,120
Sheng Yuanzhou.

89
00:04:57,399 --> 00:04:57,920
Father.

90
00:04:59,199 --> 00:05:00,079
It's about moving the car.

91
00:05:01,199 --> 00:05:02,240
Still so cowardly.

92
00:05:02,519 --> 00:05:04,040
Panicking over the smallest thing.

93
00:05:04,519 --> 00:05:05,160
Handle it, now.

94
00:05:05,959 --> 00:05:06,480
Okay.

95
00:05:11,319 --> 00:05:12,079
Zhang Xiaobei.

96
00:05:13,279 --> 00:05:14,319
Sorry to keep you waiting.

97
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:16,720
I'll finish you off right now.

98
00:05:20,560 --> 00:05:23,680
Zhang Xiaobei, go die!

99
00:05:28,079 --> 00:05:28,480
What are you doing?

100
00:05:28,879 --> 00:05:29,360
What are you all doing?

101
00:05:29,680 --> 00:05:30,199
What are you doing?

102
00:05:32,279 --> 00:05:34,360
I got your murder attempt on video.

103
00:05:34,800 --> 00:05:35,319
Watch him.

104
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:45,560
He took the syringe.

105
00:05:45,839 --> 00:05:46,639
There's no time to switch it.

106
00:05:48,560 --> 00:05:49,279
Plan B.

107
00:05:49,680 --> 00:05:51,040
You really let him inject you?

108
00:05:51,360 --> 00:05:52,360
That's way too dangerous.

109
00:05:53,560 --> 00:05:54,240
Only this way

110
00:05:55,319 --> 00:05:56,759
can we punish Sheng Shizhong

111
00:05:57,680 --> 00:05:59,120
and make him pay for what he's done.

112
00:06:01,319 --> 00:06:02,920
The risk is just too high.

113
00:06:04,000 --> 00:06:05,079
We have other ways.

114
00:06:05,879 --> 00:06:06,920
I don't want to miss this chance

115
00:06:06,920 --> 00:06:08,199
to become Zhang Xiaobei again.

116
00:06:09,519 --> 00:06:10,399
I have no choice.

117
00:06:11,079 --> 00:06:11,920
I'm counting on you.

118
00:06:13,800 --> 00:06:14,639
What if I...

119
00:06:15,399 --> 00:06:16,079
I trust you.

120
00:06:16,720 --> 00:06:17,439
Sheng Yuanzhou!

121
00:06:19,759 --> 00:06:20,120
Sheng Yuanzhou!

122
00:06:20,120 --> 00:06:21,560
I have the antidote and a doctor ready.

123
00:06:21,759 --> 00:06:23,199
Once we step out, I'll call the police.

124
00:06:23,680 --> 00:06:24,199
Hurry!

125
00:06:35,480 --> 00:06:37,439
Sheng Yuanzhou, you set me up!

126
00:06:37,759 --> 00:06:39,199
Too smart for your own good.

127
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:42,279
Hu Jin, back at you.

128
00:06:42,839 --> 00:06:44,720
You... you... Sheng Yuanzhou...

129
00:06:45,160 --> 00:06:45,439
You...

130
00:06:46,120 --> 00:06:46,439
You...

131
00:06:47,319 --> 00:06:47,680
Go!

132
00:06:49,439 --> 00:06:50,720
Doctor, this is the antidote.

133
00:06:51,199 --> 00:06:51,519
Okay.

134
00:06:57,600 --> 00:06:59,120
Good thing he got the antidote in time.

135
00:06:59,240 --> 00:07:00,120
There's no danger to his life.

136
00:07:00,560 --> 00:07:01,959
But he still needs to get to a hospital

137
00:07:02,120 --> 00:07:03,120
for a thorough checkup.

138
00:07:03,759 --> 00:07:04,199
Okay.

139
00:07:14,600 --> 00:07:15,680
You know everything now, right?

140
00:07:17,279 --> 00:07:18,120
Stealing your identity...

141
00:07:19,240 --> 00:07:20,040
That was my fault.

142
00:07:20,879 --> 00:07:21,920
But what's more important right now...

143
00:07:22,600 --> 00:07:23,360
...is Sheng Shizhong.

144
00:07:24,120 --> 00:07:25,040
He's not your Father.

145
00:07:26,480 --> 00:07:27,120
What?

146
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:31,000
Use this one more time.

147
00:07:31,319 --> 00:07:32,240
This is Sheng Shizhong's.

148
00:07:32,639 --> 00:07:32,959
No.

149
00:07:34,079 --> 00:07:34,800
More precisely,

150
00:07:35,399 --> 00:07:36,079
it's Hu Jin's.

151
00:07:36,639 --> 00:07:37,560
After you use it,

152
00:07:38,160 --> 00:07:40,240
you can read the spoon owner's memories.

153
00:07:50,199 --> 00:07:52,000
Why are you telling me this now?

154
00:07:52,639 --> 00:07:53,319
I was going to...

155
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:55,519
...use your identity as Sheng Yuanzhou

156
00:07:56,480 --> 00:07:57,959
to make more money for the family.

157
00:07:58,600 --> 00:07:59,600
But then I realized

158
00:08:00,240 --> 00:08:01,079
it wasn't about money.

159
00:08:01,759 --> 00:08:02,560
It was about the people.

160
00:08:03,120 --> 00:08:04,680
Money can be earned through hard work.

161
00:08:06,040 --> 00:08:08,079
But if we don't take down someone

162
00:08:08,079 --> 00:08:08,959
as powerful as Sheng Shizhong,

163
00:08:09,319 --> 00:08:10,800
we'll never have a good life.

164
00:08:11,480 --> 00:08:12,399
Then what do you want to do?

165
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:14,480
First, I want to find a way

166
00:08:14,839 --> 00:08:16,279
to turn you back into Sheng Yuanzhou.

167
00:08:16,639 --> 00:08:17,600
Then we will, together,

168
00:08:17,879 --> 00:08:18,600
go find Sheng Shizhong

169
00:08:18,839 --> 00:08:19,560
and end him for good.

170
00:08:20,399 --> 00:08:21,920
He's got money and power now.

171
00:08:22,199 --> 00:08:24,040
Even as Sheng Yuanzhou, I can't beat him.

172
00:08:24,480 --> 00:08:25,519
Not right now, no.

173
00:08:26,040 --> 00:08:26,720
But...

174
00:08:27,319 --> 00:08:29,480
You can return to Prosperity Group first,

175
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:30,759
and take power bit by bit.

176
00:08:31,920 --> 00:08:32,440
Then why don't we...

177
00:08:35,399 --> 00:08:36,399
...not switch back?

178
00:08:37,960 --> 00:08:39,320
You stay as Sheng Yuanzhou,

179
00:08:40,000 --> 00:08:40,799
and build up your influence.

180
00:08:41,480 --> 00:08:42,080
Me...

181
00:08:43,799 --> 00:08:44,159
Yeah.

182
00:08:45,480 --> 00:08:46,559
Actually, I noticed a long time ago

183
00:08:47,080 --> 00:08:48,480
you have a better head for business.

184
00:08:49,200 --> 00:08:50,399
Otherwise, back then I wouldn't have...

185
00:08:50,399 --> 00:08:51,600
...chosen the project you developed.

186
00:08:51,960 --> 00:08:53,360
In Sheng Yuanzhou's position,

187
00:08:53,879 --> 00:08:55,240
you've got more room to shine than I do.

188
00:08:56,279 --> 00:08:58,159
We need Sheng Shizhong to truly believe

189
00:08:58,440 --> 00:09:00,080
I'm willing to do evil with him.

190
00:09:17,519 --> 00:09:18,000
You're awake.

191
00:09:19,480 --> 00:09:20,600
You've been out for a whole day.

192
00:09:20,840 --> 00:09:22,159
Everyone thought you wouldn't wake up.

193
00:09:23,080 --> 00:09:24,360
Shut up, you Jinx.

194
00:09:27,519 --> 00:09:28,399
Where's Sheng Shizhong?

195
00:09:28,799 --> 00:09:29,840
He got arrested.

196
00:09:30,080 --> 00:09:31,000
Attempted murder.

197
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:33,320
Probably a decade or more.

198
00:09:34,840 --> 00:09:36,080
And he kept going on about

199
00:09:36,519 --> 00:09:37,399
the Key of Fate,

200
00:09:37,639 --> 00:09:38,679
switching lives and all that.

201
00:09:39,840 --> 00:09:41,240
Everyone thinks he's lost it.

202
00:09:43,200 --> 00:09:44,919
It's about time he got a taste of it.

203
00:09:45,200 --> 00:09:45,759
Yeah.

204
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:47,519
Consider it

205
00:09:48,759 --> 00:09:49,720
revenge for my Mom.

206
00:09:55,080 --> 00:09:55,759
When you come back,

207
00:09:56,519 --> 00:09:58,000
use the Key of Fate on your Dad.

208
00:09:58,720 --> 00:09:59,759
He'll get his memory back.

209
00:10:02,639 --> 00:10:03,480
Honestly...

210
00:10:04,559 --> 00:10:05,919
I haven't decided whether I should

211
00:10:05,919 --> 00:10:06,960
help him recover his memory.

212
00:10:07,440 --> 00:10:08,039
After all,

213
00:10:08,720 --> 00:10:10,120
those aren't good memories.

214
00:10:11,799 --> 00:10:12,399
But I've made up my mind.

215
00:10:12,840 --> 00:10:13,840
Whether he remembers me or not,

216
00:10:14,600 --> 00:10:15,759
I'll take care of him in his old age.

217
00:10:17,799 --> 00:10:18,600
That's great.

218
00:10:18,799 --> 00:10:20,279
We're finally back to being ourselves.

219
00:10:32,639 --> 00:10:33,200
Congrats.

220
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:35,559
You can finally be with Lin Siqi.

221
00:10:37,840 --> 00:10:39,480
You're not still hung up on her, are you?

222
00:10:41,039 --> 00:10:42,360
We cleared it up a long time ago.

223
00:10:43,080 --> 00:10:45,120
She wasn't in love with me anyway.

224
00:10:45,759 --> 00:10:47,399
And after I learned what happened to my Mom,

225
00:10:47,720 --> 00:10:48,559
I understood too

226
00:10:49,360 --> 00:10:50,480
that love you steal

227
00:10:52,039 --> 00:10:53,360
never ends well.

228
00:10:54,039 --> 00:10:55,240
Not just love.

229
00:10:55,960 --> 00:10:57,320
A stolen identity and status

230
00:10:57,559 --> 00:10:58,639
won't bring you happiness either.

231
00:10:59,639 --> 00:11:01,360
Because it's always someone else's life.

232
00:11:02,159 --> 00:11:02,879
Sheng Yuanzhou.

233
00:11:04,120 --> 00:11:05,960
From now on, let's be ourselves.

234
00:11:17,320 --> 00:11:17,960
From here on out,

235
00:11:18,840 --> 00:11:20,159
please treat this place like your home.

236
00:11:22,480 --> 00:11:23,159
Thank you.

237
00:11:30,279 --> 00:11:31,159
I feel like

238
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:33,840
I've been here before, somehow.

239
00:11:47,039 --> 00:11:47,720
Who is this?

240
00:11:50,720 --> 00:11:51,279
My mother.

241
00:12:08,039 --> 00:12:08,960
She's really beautiful.

242
00:12:15,399 --> 00:12:15,960
I'm sorry.

243
00:12:16,559 --> 00:12:17,639
I don't know what's gotten into me.

244
00:12:18,320 --> 00:12:19,759
I suddenly feel so sad.

245
00:12:24,559 --> 00:12:26,519
It's okay. It's all in the past.

246
00:12:43,559 --> 00:12:44,200
Dad, Mom!

247
00:12:46,159 --> 00:12:47,320
Xiaobei's back! Xiaobei!

248
00:12:51,720 --> 00:12:52,080
Dad!

249
00:12:52,799 --> 00:12:53,480
Son!

250
00:12:53,799 --> 00:12:54,799
Here, I'll make you some pancakes.

251
00:12:54,799 --> 00:12:55,399
No need.

252
00:12:55,399 --> 00:12:56,320
I'll do it. I will.

253
00:13:12,399 --> 00:13:13,799
Try our family's secret pancake.

254
00:13:14,039 --> 00:13:14,440
It's seriously delicious.

255
00:13:15,159 --> 00:13:15,600
Thanks.

256
00:13:16,000 --> 00:13:17,279
I don't eat crappy carbs.

257
00:13:26,559 --> 00:13:28,799
Not going back to being Sheng Yuanzhou?

258
00:13:29,600 --> 00:13:30,120
No.

259
00:13:30,879 --> 00:13:31,919
I've done what I had to do.

260
00:13:32,679 --> 00:13:33,720
I'm still Zhang Xiaobei.

261
00:13:36,559 --> 00:13:37,759
But I still want to thank you

262
00:13:38,399 --> 00:13:39,919
for playing along at the last minute.

263
00:13:41,600 --> 00:13:42,519
Don't thank me.

264
00:13:43,279 --> 00:13:45,320
I did it for that five percent

265
00:13:45,320 --> 00:13:46,840
of Prosperity Group shares, that's all.

266
00:13:47,919 --> 00:13:49,639
Got it. You're just stubborn.

267
00:13:50,679 --> 00:13:52,200
You're the coolest, okay?

268
00:13:55,360 --> 00:13:56,399
Come on, my cool friend.

269
00:13:57,159 --> 00:13:57,879
If anything comes up,

270
00:13:58,679 --> 00:13:59,720
come find me anytime.

271
00:14:00,480 --> 00:14:01,440
I'd take a bullet for you.

272
00:14:02,039 --> 00:14:02,960
Anything, anytime.

273
00:14:07,240 --> 00:14:08,440
Go make me a pancake.

274
00:14:10,840 --> 00:14:12,159
What, you actually eat this?

275
00:14:27,840 --> 00:14:29,080
Old Liu gets out of prison today.

276
00:14:30,279 --> 00:14:30,559
Sure.

277
00:14:31,200 --> 00:14:33,440
All right, I'll make you a deluxe one.

278
00:14:33,679 --> 00:14:35,000
Just wait, I'll do it myself.

279
00:14:38,960 --> 00:14:39,759
Does she eat spicy food?

280
00:14:40,039 --> 00:14:40,679
Do you want it spicy?

281
00:14:41,399 --> 00:14:42,039
No spice.

282
00:14:42,799 --> 00:14:43,159
You got it.

283
00:14:44,279 --> 00:14:44,879
No spice.

284
00:14:47,440 --> 00:14:48,440
A little bit is fine too.

285
00:14:50,360 --> 00:14:52,360
My resignation letter is on your desk.

286
00:14:53,519 --> 00:14:54,559
It's not about the pay.

287
00:14:56,240 --> 00:14:57,440
